  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Student-to-Student Lunch Project: Rural Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Rural Bangladesh, some students in almost every schools are victims of extreme poverty. They lost their fathers, mothers or both in some cases. There are no social security system in placed to rescue them. They end up living with someone else&apos;s mercy  going through very difficult time with no health care, no nutritious food and invariably they go hungry silently during long school hours. This project feeds those kids (200 students) in school, fostering their education, health and well being.</narrative>
  </description>
